msgid "PHP Functions via Schema"
msgstr "Şema Aracılığıyla PHP Fonksiyonları"

#: GatoGraphQLForWP/plugins/gatographql/src/ModuleResolvers/Extensions/PowerExtensionModuleResolver.php:97
